Interface Feed

        follows - A FollowMany object which contains a list of sources and targets

      • followMany

        void followMany(FollowMany follows)
         throws IOException,
                StreamClientException
        Follow many feed in one shot. Default activity copy limit is set to 300. Maximum 300 activities from a given source feed will be copied to the target feed.
        Parameters:
        follows - A FollowMany object which contains a list of sources and targets
        Throws:
        StreamClientException - in case of functional or server-side exception
        IOException - in case of network/socket exceptions
